#include <bits/stdc++.h>
#define ll long long
using namespace std;

vector<int> V;

int main(){

	int t;
	ll n;

	cin>>t;
	while(t--){
		V.clear();
		bool ok = true;
		int factor = 9;
		cin>>n;
		ll orignal = n;
		while(n!=1){
			if(factor == 1){
				ok = false;
				break;
			}
			if(n%factor == 0){
				V.push_back(factor);
				n/=factor;
			}
			else factor --;
		}
		if(ok){
			sort(V.begin(), V.end());
			if(orignal==1){
				cout<<11<<endl;;
				continue;
			}
			if(orignal<10)	cout<<1;
			for(int i=0;i<(int)V.size();i++)	cout<<V[i];
			cout<<endl;
		}
		else cout<<-1<<endl;
	}

	//system("pause");
	return 0;
}
